  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      test the following differences between Schinder's Target Controlled Infusion (TCI ) model and
      manually controlled infusion (MCI) :

        -  remifentanil and propofol total dose given

        -  incidence of awareness or inadequate anesthesia

        -  number of rescue dose given
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
